Name: Bellona Fossae
Name origin: Roman war goddess, wife of Mars.

Name: Felesta Fossae
Name origin: Amazon queen in Scythian epic tales.

Name: Friagabi Fossae
Name origin: Old English goddess, connected with Mars.

Name: Mist Fossae
Name origin: Norse Valkyrie. Changed to Mist Chasma.

Name: Naguchitsa Fossae
Name origin: Adygan evil warrior, old woman with iron teeth.
